Image Prompt:
Create an ethereal and majestic depiction of a radiant figure surrounded by divine light, symbolizing the concept of the one true God from Christian theology. The figure should exude a sense of omnipotence and benevolence, with symbolic elements such as a glowing halo, outstretched hands offering guidance, and a peaceful countenance that conveys divine wisdom and love. The background should be a celestial realm filled with shimmering stars and soft clouds, evoking a sense of transcendence and spiritual awe. This image should inspire reverence and contemplation of the infinite nature of the one true God in Christian belief.
